<!-- FAQ -->
<section class="section section-white">
  <div class="wrap">
    <p class="label">Common concerns</p>
    <h2 class="heading">Every concern answered.<br><em>Every risk removed.</em></h2>
    <div class="faq">

      <div class="fi open">
        <button class="fq" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">Will the quality actually be there?
          <svg width="18" height="18" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="fa"><div class="fa-inner">We don't send resumes. We send finalists. Every candidate passes: direct sourcing from proven global markets (LATAM, South Africa, Eastern Europe, Asia-Pacific), role-specific experience validation, live English and communication interviews, US business culture alignment screening, and skills assessments or portfolio review. Only candidates who meet our standards are ever introduced to you.</div></div>
      </div>

      <div class="fi">
        <button class="fq" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">What about time zones and communication?
          <svg width="18" height="18" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="fa"><div class="fa-inner">Most of our talent is based in Latin America, typically 0-2 hour time difference from US time zones. They work your hours, join your standups, and integrate into your Slack and tools exactly like a local hire. Sagan University trains every placement specifically on bridging cultural and communication gaps.</div></div>
      </div>

      <div class="fi">
        <button class="fq" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">What if it doesn't work out?
          <svg width="18" height="18" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="fa"><div class="fa-inner">All placements come with a 90-day free replacement guarantee. If the hire isn't a fit for any reason, we run a full replacement search at no additional cost. Sagan members get unlimited free replacements for voluntary departures. No time limits, no extra fees, for as long as their membership is active.</div></div>
      </div>

      <div class="fi">
        <button class="fq" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">How is this different from Upwork or a staffing agency?
          <svg width="18" height="18" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="fa"><div class="fa-inner"><strong>Focus:</strong> we specialize in remote global talent for US companies; it's not an add-on, it's our core business. <strong>Precision:</strong> we present a curated shortlist, not a flood of applications. <strong>Dual alignment:</strong> we prepare both employer and candidate for a successful working relationship. Upwork gives you freelancers. We place full-time team members who are all-in on your mission.</div></div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ─── BOOKING — single centered column: title + calendar ─── -->
<section class="book" id="book">
  <div class="book-card">
    <div class="book-card__form">
      <p class="label">Book your call</p>
      <h2 class="heading book-card__title">Get a global hiring plan<br><em>in 30 minutes.</em></h2>
      <p class="book-note">No commitment. No sales pitch. One conversation about your next hire.</p>
      <form class="lead-form" id="leadForm" novalidate>
        <label class="lead-form__label" for="leadEmail">Work email</label>
        <div class="lead-form__row">
          <input
            class="lead-form__input"
            id="leadEmail"
            name="email"
            type="email"
            inputmode="email"
            autocomplete="email"
            placeholder="you@company.com"
            required
          />
          <button class="lead-form__btn" type="submit">Book my call</button>
        </div>
        <p class="lead-form__msg" id="leadFormMsg" role="status" aria-live="polite"></p>
      </form>
      <div class="lead-form__success" id="leadFormSuccess" hidden>
        <p class="lead-form__success-title">Thanks — now book your call.</p>
        <a class="lead-form__btn" data-calendly href={cta} target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          Open my booking calendar →
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <aside class="book-card__hook">
      <span class="hook-eyebrow">What you'll walk away with</span>
      <ul class="hook-list">
        <li><i>01</i><span>The exact role your team should hire next</span></li>
        <li><i>02</i><span>Which global markets produce the best candidates for it</span></li>
        <li><i>03</i><span>Realistic salary ranges and the savings vs. a US hire</span></li>
        <li><i>04</i><span>A clear path to a vetted shortlist — or honest advice if it isn't a fit</span></li>
      </ul>
    </aside>
  </div>
</section>

